\nabla : D_1(\mathbb{R},\mathbb{C}) \rightarrow D_0(\mathbb{R}, \mathbb{C})
f \in  D_1(\mathbb{R},\mathbb{C})
c \in \mathbb{C}
\nabla(cf) = c\nabla(f).
